  "name": "Larrie &amp; the Ardies",
  "shortName": "larrie-the-ardies",
  "description": "<i>Larrie &amp; the Ardies</i> is a variant of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/arcade/mappy\">Mappy</a>. The player controls the duck Larrie, who must collect all the items lying about ten different levels. Each stage consists of a number of floors that Larrie can move between by jumping on a trampoline. Roaming the levels are the evil Ardies. Being caught by one of them means losing a life. Normally Larrie can only evade the Ardies, but by picking up power-ups or using radar stations and doors he can scare them away or even kill them. Another power-up allows him to jump between floors without using the trampoline.",
